"""Test that having a single asymmetric uncertainty fails validation.
        """
result = v.validate({'datapoints': [{'temperature': ['1000 kelvin', {
    'uncertainty-type': 'relative', 'upper-uncertainty': 0.1}]}]}, update=True)
assert not result
result = v.validate({'datapoints': [{'temperature': ['1000 kelvin', {
    'uncertainty-type': 'relative', 'lower-uncertainty': 0.1}]}]}, update=True)
assert not result
